How to run

    Install dependencies:

        pip install transformers datasets torch psutil numpy tqdm

        Optional for CSV export: pip install pandas

    Example commands:

        xquad (English subset):

            python benchmark_smollm3.py --model HuggingFaceTB/SmolLM3-3B-Instruct --dataset xquad --dataset_config xquad.en  --mode think --device cuda --limit 100

        mlqa (English QA):

            python benchmark_smollm3.py --dataset mlqa --dataset_config mlqa.en.en  --mode no_think --device cpu --limit 50

        gsm8k:

            python benchmark_smollm3.py --dataset gsm8k --mode think --device cuda --limit 50 --max_new_tokens 128

Outputs will be saved under the “outputs” directory: summary.json  plus predictions.jsonl  (and predictions.csv  if pandas is installed).
